      "writtenOn": "2021-09-01T20:39:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It works as-is for chromeos, as we don\u0027t invoke make here but link minijail through pkg-config. I like the idea of allowing an override though, I have added that to this CL.\n\nFor the longer term.. I wonder how you would feel about migrating the Makefile to meson (We already have other meson builds in ChromeOS)? I think that would make supporting other platforms and cross compilation easier, which would be really helpful for crosvm.",
      "parentUuid": "e41cc59d_d47105ec",
      "revId": "575564de7c28921541544b71209a2eb4178cca89",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889"
    },
